{
  "stem": "1415.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And like I said, my mother had borrowed money from these people in-- in-- in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we stayed with these people in Lodz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And my brother took me-- that he found out that they have a DP camp in West Germany.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I was the first one to be taken out of Poland.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But when I got to Lodz, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was still early.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was right after-- practically after liberation, which was, let's say, July or something.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I had a chance to go to school in September, in Polish school in Lodz.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's when I first started learning, really, reading and writing and everything else.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in three months I was there, I managed to skip three grades.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was very proud of myself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was 12 years old.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And my brother took me across and tried to smuggle me across from Poland, through Eastern Poland, through Eastern Germany to West Germany.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we were caught on the border by the Russians-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] smuggling.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we ended up in a camp for two weeks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But I was very lucky [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that they let us go and-- and stay in a camp.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They didn't shoot us.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
